"title": "9210: judgment, God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9210",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God judges the world by identifying and condemning sin and by vindicating and rewarding the righteous. God exercises temporal judgment on the world and on his people; final judgment will take place when Jesus Christ returns.</p>\n<h2>The nature of God's judgment</h2>\n<h3>Its certainty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:14\">ECC 12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:11\">PSA 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:17\">ECC 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:9\">ECC 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:9\">JAS 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>Its righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7-Ps9:8\">PSA 9:7–9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:6\">PSA 50:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:33\">1CH 16:33</a></p>\n<h3>Its impartiality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:7\">2CH 19:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17\">DEU 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:19\">JOB 34:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:9\">PSA 98:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:11\">ROM 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a></p>\n<h2>The purpose of God's judgment</h2>\n<h3>To display his glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:16\">ISA 5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:4\">EXO 14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:18-Isa59:19\">ISA 59:18–59:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:27\">EZK 7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:23\">EZK 38:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h3>To vindicate the righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:12-1Sam24:15\">1SA 24:12–24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:8-Ps7:9\">PSA 7:8–7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:8\">ISA 34:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:20\">JER 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:9-Jer51:10\">JER 51:9–51:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5-Rev16:7\">REV 16:5–16:7</a></p>\n<h3>To defend the weak</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:12\">PSA 140:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:1-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:1–82:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:4\">ISA 11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:16-Ezek34:22\">EZK 34:16–34:22</a></p>\n<h3>To bring salvation to his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:18\">ISA 30:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6\">EXO 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:36\">DEU 32:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:8-Ps76:9\">PSA 76:8–76:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:5-Ps105:7\">PSA 105:5–105:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:12-1Chr16:14\">1CH 16:12–16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:22\">ISA 33:22</a></p>\n<h3>To punish sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:12\">ROM 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:4-Ps1:6\">PSA 1:4–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:48\">JHN 12:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:16\">ROM 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:26-Heb10:30\">HEB 10:26–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>To turn people to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:22\">ISA 19:22</a></strong> <em>Temporal judgments may turn people to God and so save them from eternal judgment.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:33\">1KI 8:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:24\">2CH 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:13-2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:13–7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:33-Dan4:34\">DAN 4:33–4:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:5-Hos2:7\">HOS 2:5–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:29-1Cor11:32\">1CO 11:29–11:32</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment may be delayed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:1-Job24:4\">JOB 24:1–24:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:10-Ps74:11\">PSA 74:10–74:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:2-Ps94:3\">PSA 94:2–94:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2-Hab1:4\">HAB 1:2–1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:13\">HAB 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25\">ROM 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:10\">REV 6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of God's judgment</h2>\n<h3>Judgment on ungodly individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:23\">ACT 12:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:18-2Chr21:19\">2CH 21:18–21:19</a> <em>Jehoram</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:26-Dan5:28\">DAN 5:26–5:28</a> <em>Belshazzar</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:22\">REV 2:22</a> <em>Jezebel, the false prophetess</em></p>\n<h3>Judgment following particular sins</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:10-Gen4:14\">GEN 4:10–4:14</a> <em>Cain's murder of Abel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:12\">NUM 20:12</a> <em>Moses' and Aaron's disobedience</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:2\">LEV 10:1–10:2</a> <em>Nadab's and Abihu's disobedience</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:38-1Sam25:39\">1SA 25:38–25:39</a> <em>Nabal's contemptuous treatment of David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:6-2Sam6:8\">2SA 6:6–6:8</a> <em>Uzzah's handling of the ark</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23-2Kgs2:24\">2KI 2:23–2:24</a> <em>youths jeering at Elisha</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:27\">2KI 5:27</a> <em>Gehazi's greed</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:19-2Chr26:20\">2CH 26:19–26:20</a> <em>Uzziah's pride and unfaithfulness</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:10\">ACT 5:1–5:10</a> <em>Ananias' and Sapphira's lies</em></p>\n<h3>Judgment on peoples and nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:12-Joel3:13\">JOL 3:12–3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:17\">GEN 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24-Gen19:25\">GEN 19:24–19:25</a>EXO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:4-Gen7:5\">7:4–7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:4\">NUM 33:4</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:10\">1SA 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:6\">1SA 5:6</a>ISA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:12\">10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:36\">ISA 37:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:35\">2KI 19:35</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:5\">ISA 34:5</a>JER <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:12\">25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:56\">JER 51:56</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:31-Jer25:33\">JER 25:31–25:33</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment on his enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:41-Deut32:43\">DEU 32:41–32:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:3-Ps45:6\">PSA 45:3–45:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:24\">ISA 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:21-Ezek38:22\">EZK 38:21–38:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7-Rev20:10\">REV 20:7–20:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment on Israel</h2>\n<h3>God's warning of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:24\">DEU 28:15–28:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:16\">JER 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:15-Lev26:20\">LEV 26:15–26:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:33\">LEV 26:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:7-Jer11:8\">JER 11:7–11:8</a></p>\n<h3>Plagues</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:46-Num16:47\">NUM 16:46–16:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:5-Num21:9\">NUM 21:5–21:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:15\">2SA 24:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:14\">1CH 21:14</a></p>\n<h3>Drought and famine</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1\">1KI 17:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:10-Hag1:11\">HAG 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Defeat by enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1-Josh7:7\">JOS 7:1–7:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:11-Judg2:16\">JDG 2:11–2:16</a> <em>The cycle of sin, defeat and deliverance is repeated several times in Judges</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:4-2Chr28:5\">2CH 28:4–28:5</a></p>\n<h3>Exile</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:23\">2KI 17:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:17\">JER 11:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:5\">LAM 1:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:23-Ezek39:24\">EZK 39:23–39:24</a></p>\n<h2>God's final judgment on the whole earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:32\">MAT 25:31–25:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:48\">JHN 12:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:16\">ROM 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:10\">ROM 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1\">2TI 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:5\">1PE 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:11-Rev20:15\">REV 20:11–20:15</a></p>",
